Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! Travelon's anti-theft concealed carry waist pack is the safer way to carry. You'll be hands-free and secure. The rear compartment with the tamper-secure locking zipper system to help keep unwanted hands out. The holster secures to the board and can be positioned to accommodate the size of the firearm and personal draw preference of the user - ensuring a more secure draw. Air mesh padded back panel is breathable and comfortable to wear. The anti-theft features include slash-resistant construction, locking compartments, slash-resistant and locking straps to keep you and your belongings protected.
